description:
Tab is such cute guy! He reminds me of Kurt, though I think he's got a bit more blue eyed action going.
He's a confident guy for 20, and you can tell those eyes are his secret weapon with the ladies.
He was totally turned on by doing the solo, and though he says getting a blow job is his favorite thing to do with a girl, pretty sure he's gonna stick to his guns on just doin a solo.
It's a shame because you can tell he really liked being watched and showing off.
Anyway, enjoy this super cute guy! He's yummy!
title: Tab - Solo
